{"tid":1682591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（騙徒食人血饅頭）咪再幫襯HK Apocalypse (2)","createTime":"2019-10-30T06:46:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T03:20:09.000Z","uid":67347,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"884cc90a0dfa8c2542bef08883d78c4446139097","tid":1682591,"uid":67347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T06:46:05.000Z","msg":"絕對唔係分化post<br />\n因為佢地係騙徒，個底一早花哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">首先睇下佢地黑歷史先</span><br />\n<br />\n突發 有個霓虹燈牌跌落嚟 砸住咗我<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1078964\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1078964</a><br />\n<br />\n(多圖整合) 香港騙案？整霓虹燈個位巴打上次kickstarter都走咗數<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1102694\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1102694</a><br />\n<br />\n[人血饅頭] kickstarter霓虹燈撚又出嚟呃錢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1556249\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1556249</a><br />\n<br />\n[DGX團隊] 懷疑HK Apocalypse未經授權拎願榮光去賣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675418\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675418</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">而家佢地就不斷推反送中周邊產品搵食</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OeAwpWR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOeAwpWR.png&h=a77477ff&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s2NbpWR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs2NbpWR.png&h=ff9b64b7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NpaPV3x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNpaPV3x.jpg&h=72221753&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">價錢：<br />\n- 單個 : $48<br />\n- 10個或以上 :每個 $32<br />\n#收益扣除成本直接撥捐星火<br />\n.<br />\n交收方法：平郵/順豐站到付 (5個或以上會用順豐到付)<br />\n.<br />\n有任何問題請 whatsapp: 5980 9046</span><br />\n<br />\n而佢地聲稱收益扣除成本會捐612同星火<br />\n最後，佢地係有捐<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">捐左一次，話賣得2千幾個，仲要捐$10/個</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dqth4Xa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDqth4Xa.png&h=6edccdd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">即係話成本要$22-38/個</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁成本係咪包左海量facebook廣告，租金同「人工」呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢間野由kickstarter 開始已經呃左好多錢<br />\n好多苦主受害<br />\n而家仲要消費場運動<br />\n食人血饅頭<br />\n屌你老母啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">大家可以考慮係佢facebook 留言既<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/neonlightinhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fneonlightinhk%2F&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt380oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=c09458fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/neonlightinhk/</a><br />\n不過佢地刪comment 同block你既速度係好快</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">暫時諗到既都係report佢page<br />\n同繼續開post俾大家知<br />\n可以既話大家都幫手share呢個post上facebook</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">最後<br />\n記得112出黎</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W4WvFvR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW4WvFvR.png&h=f44f4812&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a91d70200b714efbd683577006024bda79e5c6f","tid":1682591,"uid":67347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T06:46:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55a91c558148e7cfc07da458157fbe6f72b04a50","tid":1682591,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T06:46:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zyBfyPB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzyBfyPB.jpg&h=2708f4ca&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"db0f30a425198a11f18a75fd5c84bf30e9dab751","tid":1682591,"uid":67347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T06:47:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b161c00ccb3c487b3bd49502076724a5cbcd1037","tid":1682591,"uid":67347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T06:47:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e3edf77156906177993423356a9bd3597660d99","tid":1682591,"uid":67347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T06:47:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ccbc8e6f90b3f7a82e200c0b3424bf94901faf2","tid":1682591,"uid":67347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T06:49:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"48d657d70ab44991d00c84b4fedf580f8772800e","tid":1682591,"uid":67347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T06:49:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8fa066ab5c46bfd178cc0541fba18a95b6e5a7d5","tid":1682591,"uid":67347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T06:49:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a1da3e0deb7c1abc2925df248160d8b500d2def3","tid":1682591,"uid":67347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T06:50:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3e9ab67c4be1e42b2be8b189f71b3fc1564ff338","tid":1682591,"uid":67347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T06:50:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d822a760d5118483532fce6669bc7727ef171314","tid":1682591,"uid":67347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T06:50:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e71b96dc828fc2751dda804167a6c77595ca9d04","tid":1682591,"uid":67347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T06:51:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"81ba6c61080e5b865f213709a451b17f9be34cc9","tid":1682591,"uid":67347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T06:52:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17df3d48228af066ef9e83d6a7a9b77cfcbf12fc","tid":1682591,"uid":67347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,